<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Three<rs type="objectType"> frieze</rs> blocks: a, in two fragments (length, together, <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.78</measure>) has a space with a small moulding above, at the left end, before the text; it has the assembly mark <foreign lang="grc"><unclear reason="damage">Η</unclear>Α</foreign>. The other two blocks have no assembly marks; b, broken to the left, is <measure precision="circa" dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.75</measure>; c, broken at the right, is <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.47</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in three lines on the fascia.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025-0.03</measure>; dot for stop; ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign>, <foreign lang="grc">ΗΜ</foreign>, l. 1; <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign>, <foreign lang="grc">ΜΗΝ</foreign>, l. 3</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>

<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">institutions</rs>)</p>
<p>
</p>
